data.description: Make an appointment to view this Beautiful 3 bedrooms, 2 Bathroom Home with 2 dining areas, 2 car garage with rear entry. The master bedroom is oversized and includes a sitting area, along with a large walk-in closet. The entire house is equipped with two-inch faux wood blinds, and each room features ceiling fans. Stainless steel appliances, including a side-by-side refrigerator, are negotiable and many more upgrades. The backyard boasts a covered patio. Enjoy community amenities such as a pool, playground, hiking trails, and walking trails. The home is pre-wired for a security system. Experience a blend of country living and city convenience in the Bear Creek community. Additional features include a radiant barrier, low-E windows, and a 14-seer AC system.
